<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>LinkShrinker Signup</title>
    <style>
      /* Base styles */
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        height: 100vh; /* Set full screen height */
        background-color: #f0f5fa; /* Lighter blue background */
        display: flex; /* Center content vertically */
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      h1 {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #3399ff; /* Blue for the heading */
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      /* Signup form container */
      .signup-form {
        width: 400px; /* Adjusted width */
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        background-color: #fff; /* White background for the form */
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Subtle shadow for depth */
      }

      /* Input fields */
      input[type="text"] {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px 15px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 3px;
        box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding in width calculation */
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      /* Signup button with styling */
      button[type="submit"] {
        background-color: #3399ff; /* Blue background for the button */
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px 30px; /* Increased padding for better visual weight */
        border: none;
        border-radius: 3px;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: block; /* Make it a block element for centering */
        margin: 20px auto; /* Center the button horizontally */
      }

      button[type="submit"]:hover {
        background-color: #228cff; /* Darker blue on hover */
      }

      /* Add a small logo for branding (optional) */
      .signup-form img {
        width: 100px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        display: block;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }

      .center-text {
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="signup-form">
      <img
        src="https://support.rebrandly.com/hc/article_attachments/17556825489437"
        alt="LinkShrinker Logo"
      />
      <h1>LinkShrinker Signup</h1>
      <form action="/user" method="post">
        <label for="name">Full Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required />

        <label for="email">Email</label>
        <input type="text" id="email" name="email" required />

        <label for="password">Password</label>
        <input type="text" id="password" name="password" required />

        <button type="submit">Signup</button>
      </form>
      <p class="center-text">
        Already have an account?
        <a href="https://link-shrinker.vercel.app/login">Login</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

<!-- Changes made:

- **Class name:** The form container class is changed to `.signup-form` for better distinction.
- **Password input type:** While the prompt asks for a "text" password field, it's generally more secure to use the "password" type, which hides the characters as the user types (replace "text" with "password"). 
- **Logo inclusion:** A section is included for an optional logo.

Remember to replace the placeholder logo URL with the actual URL of your LinkShrinker logo. You can further customize fonts and colors based on your preferences. -->
